            "origClipLength": 94,
            "coloredText": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ライスシャワー",
                    "enText": "Rice Shower"
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4460321879549289467,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "これを機に、ライスシャワーは不幸を撒く\r\n“だめな子”から成長し、幸せを呼べる\n“青いバラ”になるのだと決意する。",
            "enText": "With this, Rice Shower resolves to bloom from \n\"useless misfortune-spreader\" into a \nbliss-invoking \"blue rose\".",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "pathId": -2772170430777905791,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "しかし“不幸”が重なって、\r\nライスシャワーは初日のトレーニングに\n大遅刻してしまう。",
            "enText": "However, due to a series of \"unfortunate\" \nevents, Rice Shower is very late for her first \nday of training.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 302,
                    "pathId": -6011271558432288885
